Title: fantom5_cage
Description: Cultured cells obtained from FANTOM5 consortium containing only neuron and astrocyte composition

Title: IP_immunopurified_human_brain
Description: Immunopurified whole-cells from the human cortex from Zhang et al  (2016)

Title: MM_immunopurified_mouse_brain
Description: Immunopurified whole-cells from the mouse cortex from Zhang et al (2015)

Title: CA_CellAtlas_snRNAseq
Description: Single-nucleus RNA-sequencing of the post-mortem human brain from the Human Cell Atlas

Title: LK_snRNAseq
Description: Single-nucleus RNA-sequencing of the post-mortem human adult frontal cortex from Lake et al (2018)

Title: TS_scRNAseq
Description: Single-cell RNA-sequencing from the adult mouse cortex from Tasic et al ()

Title: NG_snRNAseq
Description: Single-nucleus RNA-sequencing from the adult human post-mortem prefrontal cortex from Nagy et al

Title: DM_scRNAseq
Description: Single-cell RNA-sequencing data from the middle temporal gyrus generated by Darmanis et al (2015)

Title: VL_snRNAseq
Description: Single-nucleus RNA-seqeucning from post-mortem adult human brain from Velmeshev et al

Title: MultiBrain
Description: Signature generated by quantile-normalising and averaging RPKM expression levels of CA, IP, DM, NG and VL sigantures
